# 3D Models Directory

Place your mechanical design files here:

- `frame_base.step` - Main base frame
- `frame_base.stl` - 3D printable base frame
- `pan_platform.step` - Pan rotation platform
- `pan_platform.stl`
- `tilt_arm.step` - Tilt rotation arm  
- `tilt_arm.stl`
- `camera_bracket.step` - Camera mounting bracket
- `camera_bracket.stl`
- `laser_mount.step` - Laser module mount
- `laser_mount.stl`
- `servo_bracket.step` - Servo mounting brackets
- `servo_bracket.stl`

## Design Software

Recommended tools:
- FreeCAD (free, open-source)
- Fusion 360 (free for students/startups)
- OpenSCAD (parametric design)
- Blender (general 3D modeling)

## Print Settings (for FDM 3D printing)

- **Nozzle Temp**: 210-220°C (PETG)
- **Bed Temp**: 60-80°C (PETG)
- **Layer Height**: 0.2mm
- **Infill**: 15-20%
- **Orientation**: Check for minimal supports needed
